title: By the end of the call have a very loud beep notification that can't be disabled, how to disable?
content: By the end of the call have a very loud beep notification that can't be disabled, I have read about the snapchat bug but I haven't snapchat installed also i disabled permissions to phone and microphone almost to all apps and still have this annoying beep, how can I disable it?
